
---

## 12) Dockerfile

### `Dockerfile`

```dockerfile
FROM python:3.11-slim

WORKDIR /app

# System deps (optional but safe for pdf libs)
RUN apt-get update && apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
    build-essential \
 && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

COPY requirements.txt .
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt

COPY app ./app
COPY web ./web
COPY data ./data
COPY PROMPTS.md README.md ./

EXPOSE 8080

# Run server (assumes you've already ingested; alternatively ingest at startup if you want)
CMD ["uvicorn", "app.main:app", "--host", "0.0.0.0", "--port", "8080"]
